---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const pageTitle = "Terms of Service";
const pageDescription = "Terms and conditions for using Vital Health NZ telehealth services.";
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <Navigation />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-primary section-padding">
    <div class="container-max text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
              <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-neutral-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Please read these terms carefully before using our telehealth services
        </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Terms Content -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-max">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing and using Vital Health NZ's telehealth services, you accept and agree to be bound by 
          these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing or using our website, joining our waitlist, or interacting with our services, 
          you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you disagree with any part of these terms, 
          you may not access our services.
        </p>

        <h3>Service Description</h3>
        <p>
          Vital Health NZ provides telehealth medical consultations for medical weight management and 
          metabolic health assessment. Our services are delivered by qualified, 
          MCNZ-registered doctors through secure video consultations.
        </p>

        <h3>Eligibility</h3>
        <p>To use our services, you must:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Be at least 18 years old</li>
          <li>Be located in New Zealand during consultations</li>
          <li>Have a valid email address</li>
          <li>Have access to appropriate technology for video consultations</li>
          <li>Provide accurate and complete health information</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Medical Disclaimer</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Service Limitations:</strong> Vital Health is a telehealth-only service. We do not offer face-to-face consultations or in-person appointments. Our services are designed for routine healthcare consultations and ongoing health management.
        </p>
        <p>
          While our doctors are qualified and experienced, telehealth may not be appropriate for all medical 
          conditions. If a physical examination or hands-on assessment is required, you will be advised to see another medical provider who can provide in-person care.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Specialist Services:</strong> We provide specialist lifestyle medicine services focused on medical weight management 
          . Your regular GP remains responsible for your 
          ongoing general healthcare needs and primary care coordination.
        </p>

        <h3>Appointment Cancellation Policy</h3>
        <p>
          We require 24 hours notice for appointment cancellations or rescheduling. Late cancellations or 
          no-shows may result in a cancellation fee. We understand that emergencies happen and will work 
          with you on a case-by-case basis.
        </p>

        <h3>Payment Terms</h3>
        <p>
          Payment is required at the time of booking or before your consultation. We accept major credit 
          cards and online payment methods. All fees are in New Zealand dollars and include GST.
        </p>

        <h3>Refund and Cancellation Policy</h3>
        <p>
          We offer the following refund and cancellation terms:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Cancellation 24+ hours before appointment:</strong> Full refund</li>
          <li><strong>Cancellation less than 24 hours before appointment:</strong> 50% refund</li>
          <li><strong>No-show appointments:</strong> No refund</li>
          <li><strong>Technical issues on our end:</strong> Full refund or rescheduling</li>
          <li><strong>Medical issue preventing attendance:</strong> Full refund with documentation</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Refunds will be processed within 5-10 business days to the original payment method.
        </p>

        <h3>User Responsibilities</h3>
        <p>You agree to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide accurate and complete health information</li>
          <li>Participate actively in your consultations</li>
          <li>Follow prescribed treatment plans and recommendations</li>
          <li>Maintain the confidentiality of your login credentials</li>
          <li>Use our services only for their intended purpose</li>
          <li>Not attempt to access other users' information</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Limitation of Liability</h3>
        <p>
          Vital Health NZ's liability is limited to the amount paid for the specific service in question. 
          We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of 
          our services.
        </p>

        <h3>Intellectual Property</h3>
        <p>
          All content on our website, including text, graphics, logos, and software, is the property of 
          Vital Health NZ and is protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws.
        </p>

        <h3>Privacy and Data Protection</h3>
        <p>
          Your privacy is important to us. Please review our Privacy Policy to understand how we collect, 
          use, and protect your information. By using our services, you consent to our privacy practices.
        </p>

        <h3>Changes to Terms</h3>
        <p>
          We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes 
          by posting the new terms on our website and updating the effective date.
        </p>

        <h3>Governing Law</h3>
        <p>
          These Terms of Service are governed by the laws of New Zealand. Any disputes will be resolved 
          in the courts of New Zealand.
        </p>

        <h3>Contact Information</h3>
        <p>
          If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> admin@healthhealth.co.nz</p>
          <p><strong>Address:</strong> Vital Health, PO Box 2293, South Dunedin, Dunedin 9012</p>
          <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> We aim to respond within 5 business days</p>
        </div>




      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

